---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn more about Autopilot Reviews and our honest product testing process.">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">About Autopilot Reviews</h1>
		
		<div class="prose prose-indigo prose-lg text-slate-700 mx-auto">
			<p>
				Welcome to <strong>Autopilot Reviews</strong>. Our mission is simple: to help you make informed buying decisions without the stress of endless research.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
			<p>
				We believe that shopping should be easy. In a world of infinite choices and paid sponsorships, finding an honest opinion is harder than ever. That's why we created Autopilot Reviews—a place where data meets experience.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">How We Review</h2>
			<p>
				Our team of researchers and writers spends hours analyzing product specifications, reading verified customer feedback, and comparing performance metrics. We don't just look at the price tag; we look at the value.
			</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
				<li><strong>Objective Testing:</strong> We focus on measurable data points.</li>
				<li><strong>Honest Pros & Cons:</strong> Every product has flaws, and we'll tell you what they are.</li>
				<li><strong>Expert Comparison:</strong> We compare products against their direct competitors to find the true winner.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
			<p>
				To keep our site free for readers, we participate in various affiliate marketing programs. This means we may get paid a commission on sales of those products we write about. 
			</p>
			<p>
				However, our editorial content is not influenced by advertisers or affiliate partnerships. We only recommend products we genuinely believe in. Our first priority is always you, the reader.
			</p>

			<div class="bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-2xl mt-12 border border-indigo-100">
				<h3 class="text-indigo-900 font-bold text-xl mb-4">Contact Us</h3>
				<p class="text-indigo-800">
					Have a question about a review or want us to test a specific product? Reach out to us at <span class="font-bold">hello@autopilotreviews.com</span>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>